quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  111,1,"Mu Hadith eri mu kitabo kya Bukhari Nabbi yagenda ku Batwhahu naakuba wuuli abantu bangi bajja nga balowooza nti waliyo ebya maguzi, Nabbi bweyatandika okubabuulira ebikwata ku Katonda, Abu Lahbi naakasuka e mikono nga bwagamba nti kino kyotukunganyirizza era kyotuyitidde? Zikirira. Katonda kwe kumwanukula mu ssura eno naagamba nti: (Gizikirire e mikono gya Abu Lahbi (gyawuuba), era ddala yenna yazikirira"
  111,2,"Eby'obugaggabwe tebimugasizza, wadde n’ebirala bye yafuna, (nga e kitiibwa)"
  111,3,Ajja kwesonseka mu muliro ogubumbujja
  111,4,Ne mukyalawe omwetissi w’enku (naye bwatyo)
  111,5,Nga mu nsingoye mulimu omuguwa omulange